data.description: Come enjoy the serene lake life surrounded by nature in this charming ranch style 3 bedroom 2 bath home, with a double car garage, that sits on 1.02 acre of land with a boat ramp area just around the corner. Imagine sunny Texas mornings or calm evenings on the lake available for you year round with no HOA! It is located just a short drive to Mathis, Beeville, Sinton and Corpus Christi! Don't miss out on the opportunity to own your own slice of Texas by Lake Corpus Christi!
